        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Epipenaeon latifrons Bourdon, 1979, reference female (CIEPE550303) (A–I), reference male (CIEPE550304) (J–L). (A) Dorsal view; (B) Ventral view; (C) Right maxilliped, external view; (D) Palp of right maxilliped; (E) Right side of barbula; (F) Right oostegite 1, external view; (G) Right oostegite 1, internal view; (H) Right pereopod 1; (I) Right pereopod 7; (J) Dorsal view; (K) Ventral view; (L) Left antenna and antennule. Scale: 1 mm for A, B; 0.38 mm for C; 0.18 mm for D; 0.50 mm for E, F, G; 0.14 mm for H; 0.15 mm for I; 0.27 mm for J, K; 0.14 mm for L." ;
